Package: emissions
Title: Emissions (One Line, Title Case)
Version: 0.0.0.9000
Authors@R: 
    person("Qiuyuan", "Chen", , "qche0055@student.monash.edu", role = c("aut", "cre"),
           comment = c(ORCID = "YOUR-ORCID-ID"))
Description: The emissions package provides tools for exploring global carbon emissions data from major companies, enabling users to interactively analyze and visualize emissions trends across different time periods. This package includes a user-friendly Shiny app that allows for the dynamic exploration of emissions data by selecting specific companies and year ranges, making it easier to track changes in emissions over time.
